---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Excavation & Earthworks Pakenham | Bobcat & Mini-Excavator Hire"
  description="Excavation and earthworks in Pakenham, Officer, Berwick. Bobcat & mini-excavator works, cut-and-fill, drainage, levelling for sheds, driveways and pools. Free quote — (03) 9003 0223."
  canonical="https://pakenhamretainingwalls.com.au/services/excavation-earthworks/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Excavation &amp; Earthworks</span>
      <h1>Excavation, earthworks &amp; <span class="accent">site preparation</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Bobcat and mini-excavator works across Pakenham and the Cardinia Shire. Cut-and-fill,
        levelling, drainage, footings, trenches &mdash; the dirt work behind almost every
        backyard project.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">What we move</span>
      <h2>Earthworks done with the right machine.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <p>
          Most "earthworks" jobs in Pakenham fail because someone tries to do them with the
          wrong machine. Too small and you&rsquo;re there for a week; too big and you can&rsquo;t fit
          through the side gate. We run a 2.5t and a 5t mini-excavator and a bobcat &mdash;
          the right combo for residential blocks.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Common jobs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cut-and-fill for shed pads</strong> &mdash; flat, compacted base for a Stratco-type shed or pole barn.</li>
          <li><strong>Driveway preparation</strong> &mdash; cut to grade, base material spread &amp; compacted, ready for concrete or paving.</li>
          <li><strong>Pool excavation</strong> &mdash; dig-out for fibreglass or concrete pools (we work with all major Pakenham pool installers).</li>
          <li><strong>Drainage trenches</strong> &mdash; ag-pipe, stormwater, or sub-soil drains across the back yard or under the house.</li>
          <li><strong>Site clearing</strong> &mdash; small tree removal, stump-out, levelling, and rubbish removal for new builds and renovations.</li>
          <li><strong>Trenches for retaining walls</strong> &mdash; for our own work and for other builders who need a footing dug.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Spoil &amp; fill</h3>
        <p>
          We can take the spoil away or leave it on-site. We can also bring in clean fill,
          crushed rock, or topsoil. All measured by the tonne, all priced upfront in the quote.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">DBYD &amp; underground services</h3>
        <p>
          Every job in Pakenham starts with a Dial Before You Dig request and a service
          locate where there&rsquo;s any chance of hitting buried gas, water, NBN, or power.
          That&rsquo;s our cost, not yours.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cost</h3>
        <p>
          Earthworks is priced by the hour or the job depending on what&rsquo;s involved.
          For most residential jobs, expect $120&ndash;$180/hr for the machine + operator,
          or a fixed quote for any job over half a day. Hourly rates include the
          machine, fuel, and operator &mdash; no hidden extras.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other services.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/timber-retaining-walls/"><h3>Timber sleeper</h3><p>Most economical, 15&ndash;40 year lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/concrete-sleeper-walls/"><h3>Concrete sleeper</h3><p>50+ year lifespan, ideal for taller walls.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/block-retaining-walls/"><h3>Block / masonry</h3><p>Premium look, long lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/"><h3>Back to home</h3><p>Pakenham retaining walls overview.</p><span class="svc-link">Home &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free earthworks quote.</h2>
        <p>Tell us what you&rsquo;re building &mdash; we&rsquo;ll quote the dirt work.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Quote online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
